1:1 COMMENT "# unit_multiparam.z -- a generic unit is generic over ALL its parameters, not"
1:78 EOL "\n"
2:1 COMMENT "# just the first. Every member is typed by its own arg (combine's a: t, b: u),"
2:79 EOL "\n"
3:1 COMMENT "# and `match` dissects over any parameter -- here the SECOND, u. Two"
3:69 EOL "\n"
4:1 COMMENT "# instantiations sharing the first arg but differing in the second stay distinct."
4:82 EOL "\n"
